data.database_description: The database is designed to manage and track data related to music albums, artists, employees, customers, genres, invoices, media types, tracks, invoice lines, playlists, and playlist tracks. It captures detailed information about artists and their albums, including associated genres, tracks, and media formats. Employee records are maintained with hierarchical reporting structures, supporting customer support roles linked to specific sales data through invoices. Customers are tracked along with their interactions via invoicing, while the system also handles music playlists that include various tracks. The database supports relationships between these entities to facilitate comprehensive management of a music-related business operation.
